&lt;li&gt;Travel to support events and activations as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales &amp;amp; Activation Support&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the sales team on customer-facing events, activations, and lead-generation opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help coordinate event materials, sales collateral, giveaways, signage, booth assets, equipment, and activation setup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure sales team members have the information, materials, and logistical support they need before and during events.&lt;/li&gt;
