&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protect your community while building your career.&lt;/strong&gt; At CPI Security, we don&#39;t just sell alarms; we provide peace of mind. As a Residential Sales Representative in our Charlotte market, you’ll join an industry leader with a culture built on growth, stability, and helping others.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target Earnings:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;$60,000 - $90,000+&lt;/strong&gt; (Base salary guarantee + uncapped commissions)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Perks:&lt;/strong&gt; Company fuel card, iPhone, iPad, and a &lt;strong&gt;Free Monitored Security System&lt;/strong&gt; after 90 days.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Future Growth:&lt;/strong&gt; Comprehensive leadership development and ongoing training to move you up the ladder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt; Full Medical, Dental, Vision, 401(k) with company match, and generous PTO/Paid Holidays.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
