&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Generation:&lt;/strong&gt; Utilize company-provided leads and proactive prospecting tools to build a robust sales pipeline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
